      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  either normal-weight (BMI 18-25kg/m2) or overweight/obese (BMI 28-50kg/m2) with either
             central or peripheral fat deposits based on DEXA

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Iron Supplement or antibiotic intake within 2 weeks before study start

          -  diagnosed chronic disease or gastrointestinal disorders

          -  regular use of medication (except contraceptives)

          -  pregnancy

